column5: Idk how to use this app I jus googled things and some of these story’s came up ! I guess I’ll know and or c your message when it pops up 🤷🏻‍♀️
Right now ! Laying down ! Battling depression! Feeling unloved ! No one will ever take me seriously and be with me. !

I’m so tired of feeling depressed ! Tired of wasting my time in relationships that will never work! Tired of being stuck and not getting anywhere in life ! I really jus wanna end my life! 
I will never find love ! No one will ever love me and be serious ! People like to waste my time ! Smh
